data.description: Privacy abounds in this 4-bed, 2-bath, 2,288 square foot home, completely surrounded by 7 acres of mature trees, trails, deer stands, and wildlife, with state-owned land directly behind the property. Two bedrooms and one bathroom are on each level, with a rec room and laundry in the lower level. Upstairs, the living room opens up to the eat-in kitchen that offers lots of storage space and access to the large deck overlooking the back yard. Outside, two small storage sheds are flanked by a 24 x 60 garage, part of which functions as a heated workshop. In addition to fruit trees on the property, raised gardens provide an opportunity to grow your own food. This home offers plenty of privacy, yet is just a short 7-minute drive from town. Come take a look today!
